{"tid":1998422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[仇議員又可以出動] 團體抗議美國干涉香港事務　一度逾四人同場","createTime":"2020-05-02T11:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T11:54:49.000Z","uid":28435,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d3340d1a59d856e25880b490f7a6d2db1e70bfcb","tid":1998422,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62qGhzM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62qGhzM.jpg&h=3436f8ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多個團體分批四人一組，半小時內先後到美國領事館抗議，警方未有阻止。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會鄧家彪等人，到美國領事館抗議，指美國不應干涉基本法廿三條立法，他們將請願信放到領事館門外後散去，半個小時內共有三個團體，先後分批到領事館，就相同的議題抗議，其間一度有超過四人同場，有警員上前了解，其中一人離開，警員未有阻止。<br />\n<br />\n五一勞動節當日，工黨及社民連遊行到政府總部，他們分成每組四人，相距一點五米，警方當時向他們發出告票，指他們違反限聚令。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長陳肇始未有正面回應，警方有否不公平濫用「限聚令」，只是說執法人員會視乎情況執法。"},{"pid":"ad8ed63a1880ab3505e9061b9ce4e72a00861c46","tid":1998422,"uid":10201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:18:26.000Z","msg":"又黎互相包庇"},{"pid":"64fa895d49aac40be2e2c452702dca047d4de5c8","tid":1998422,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:18:58.000Z","msg":"#梁國雄"},{"pid":"00286d66bf1c5618ff18cec40a00a2334b8d33a9","tid":1998422,"uid":69289,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:19:56.000Z","msg":"直頭有埋狗隻護送，知法犯法咪呢啲"},{"pid":"30ed56bbb53ec69d6d59609a90f30657965c1d0a","tid":1998422,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd26fd6f418028af1b4965d33bc174c8aaf0b30","tid":1998422,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:21:54.000Z","msg":"支那狗唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那狗有特權架嘛，拉咩撚？"},{"pid":"59ddae8fb8d68e88a2c72f90f447131239119f5c","tid":1998422,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime